&lt;li&gt;Set up and break down equipment before and after lessons and clinics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Promote participation and help retain players through exceptional customer service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current with pickleball teaching methods, trends, and best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
